- .gitignore
- ReadME

## Getting Started
### 1. Clone the repository

bash
git clone https://github.com/Werapat-rtn/Crypto.git
cd CryptoDB

### 2. docker-compose
bash
docker-compose up -d

### 3. Install dependencies
bash
npm install

### 4. Configure .env
.env
DB_NAME=Crypto
DB_USER=werapat
DB_PASS=ZNEB0706
DB_HOST=localhost
PORT=3000

### 5. Seed the Database
bash
node seeders/seed.js
  
  This will:
   - Create mock data users
   - Register 4 crypto assets: BTC, ETH, XRP, DOGE
   - Create wallets linked to the user

### 6. Run The Server and Test api
bash
npm run dev

GET http://localhost:3000/users/1/wallets